    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的小型类银河恶魔城之作《小小危险地牢》以完全重建冒险的形态回归！引导小小寻宝猎人提米穿过一个比原版游戏中大两倍的地牢！探索新的谜题、物品和秘密，并与凶猛的新Boss战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新图像和配乐！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《小小危险地牢》已进行完全重建，重制版具有更好的操纵、崭新的彩色图像和全新音轨！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩建的新地城！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras_big/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢中加入了新的房间，给予了玩家更多探索空间和可重复游玩性。新的地牢比原版游戏中的地牢要大上两倍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >凶猛的新Boss！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中添加了全新的Boss战，找到并与5个可怕的Boss生物作战吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未知的新秘密！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.apng?t=1741277959\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" class=\"bb_img\" width=568 height=320 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密关卡和神秘的新宝藏都隐藏在地牢之中！如果发现了所有秘密，会发生什么事呢……？</p>",
